    <item>
      <title>AEP 聘请 Sempra 前首席财务官，助力公用事业公司应对需求激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/aep-hires-former-sempra-cfo-as-utility-navigates-demand-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国电力公司 (American Electric Power Co.) 任命 Sempra 前首席财务官 Trevor Mihalik 担任同一职务，因为作为美国最大的公用事业公司之一，该公司正面临电力需求增长的问题，并希望改善与监管机构的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/aep-hires-former-sempra-cfo-as-utility-navigates-demand-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利将在债务发行热潮中发行欧元和美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/chile-taps-global-debt-markets-amid-emerging-market-sale-deluge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利正在通过发售美元和欧元计价的债券进入国际债务市场，与墨西哥和匈牙利等国一样，本周有望成为债券发行繁忙的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/chile-taps-global-debt-markets-amid-emerging-market-sale-deluge</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 12:18:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
