      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 09:40:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比利时启动欧洲债券发售热潮，订单数量创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/belgium-kicks-off-european-debt-sale-rush-with-a-10-year-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比利时通过银行出售的 10 年期债券吸引了创纪录的需求，因为投资者争相在欧洲央行进一步降低利率之前锁定六个月来的最高收益率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/belgium-kicks-off-european-debt-sale-rush-with-a-10-year-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:25:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
