      <title>数据抑制美联储押注，股市下跌，收益率上升：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新经济数据加剧了人们对美联储在通胀压力下本月将维持利率不变的猜测，导致股市下跌，债券收益率上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
